    <briefdescription>
<para>Layer that displays and formats a text string. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><image type="html" name="text_layer.png" inline="yes"></image>
 <image type="latex" name="text_layer.png" inline="yes"></image>
